<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>智能新闻| smithsonianmag.com</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/rss/smart-news/</link><description>智能新闻的 RSS 提要</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 15:25:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>这种色彩缤纷的鹦鹉在过去的一个世纪里只见过一次。观鸟者刚刚在未开发的印度尼西亚森林中重新发现了它</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-colorful-parakeet-had-been-seen-only-once-over-the-past-century-birders-just-rediscovered-it-in-an-unexplored-indonesian-forest-180988907/</link><description>蓝额澳洲鹦鹉于 20 年代首次通过七个标本被描述，自 2014 年以来就再也没有被发现过。最近徒步旅行的观鸟者拍摄了这种稀有鸟类的照片，并捕捉到了第一批已知的其叫声的录音</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/this-colorful-parakeet-had-been-seen-only-once-over-the-past-century-birders-just-rediscovered-it-in-an-unexplored-indonesian-forest-180988907/</guid></item><item><title>一艘“几乎难以置信”的沉船令挪威考古学家震惊，船上装满了完好无损的瓷器和奢侈品</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-shipwreck-almost-beyond-belief-stunned-archaeologists-in-norway-with-its-cargo-of-intact-porcelain-dishes-and-luxury-goods-180988910/</link><description>到目前为止，考古学家已从这艘 18 世纪的沉船中发现了 40 件文物，可能还会发现数千件宝藏</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 22:07:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/a-shipwreck-almost-beyond-belief-stunned-archaeologists-in-norway-with-its-cargo-of-intact-porcelain-dishes-and-luxury-goods-180988910/</guid></item><item><title>银河系中心的超大质量黑洞似乎在吹风——正如科学家长期以来的理论那样</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-supermassive-black-hole-at-the-heart-of-our-galaxy-seems-to-be-blowing-wind-just-as-scientists-long-theorized-180988908/</link><description>自 20 世纪 70 年代以来，科学家们一直在寻找这种微风的证据。他们已经看到来自其他黑洞的强烈风，但他们一直在努力观察银河系中心的黑洞</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 19:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/the-supermassive-black-hole-at-the-heart-of-our-galaxy-seems-to-be-blowing-wind-just-as-scientists-long-theorized-180988908/</guid></item><item><title>144 年来，这座大教堂一直矗立在巴塞罗那之上。中央塔现已竣工，教皇利奥十四世准备访问</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/sagrada-familia-basilica-has-been-rising-above-barcelona-for-144-years-with-its-central-tower-now-complete-pope-leo-XIV-prepares-to-visit-180988906/</link><description>当安东尼·高迪（Antoni Gaudí）对圣家堂（Sagrada Família）提出雄心勃勃的愿景时，他知道自己无法活着看到它的竣工。建筑师去世一百年后，最高的塔已达到顶峰</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 19:14:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/sagrada-familia-basilica-has-been-rising-above-barcelona-for-144-years-with-its-central-tower-now-complete-pope-leo-XIV-prepares-to-visit-180988906/</guid></item><item><title>在二战领袖温斯顿·丘吉尔去世后首次举办的英国大型回顾展上，令人惊讶地一睹他的消遣——绘画</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/catch-a-surprising-glimpse-at-wwii-leader-winston-churchills-pastime-painting-at-the-first-major-british-retrospective-since-his-death-180988905/</link><description>伦敦展出的 50 多幅油画详细描述了首相远离战争、演讲和政治的安静时刻</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 17:49:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/catch-a-surprising-glimpse-at-wwii-leader-winston-churchills-pastime-painting-at-the-first-major-british-retrospective-since-his-death-180988905/</guid></item><item><title>科学家研究火蝾螈已有 250 多年的历史。他们刚刚发现这些生物在紫外线下会发光</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-have-been-studying-these-salamanders-for-more-than-250-years-they-just-discovered-the-creatures-glow-under-uv-light-180988900/</link><description>火蝾螈是欧洲研究最深入的两栖动物之一，具有生物荧光，这意味着它们可以吸收外部光源的一种波长的光，然后以另一种波长重新发射光</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 15:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-have-been-studying-these-salamanders-for-more-than-250-years-they-just-discovered-the-creatures-glow-under-uv-light-180988900/</guid></item><item><title>是什么决定了蜜蜂的版税？一项研究表明，皇后区不仅需要独特的饮食，还需要专门建造的王室</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/what-determines-royalty-among-honeybees-not-just-a-distinct-diet-queens-also-need-specially-built-regal-chambers-a-study-suggests-180988899/</link><description>未来蚁后成长的花生状隔间似乎在发育中发挥着重要作用。蜡与蜂巢其他部分的蜡具有化学和物理差异</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/what-determines-royalty-among-honeybees-not-just-a-distinct-diet-queens-also-need-specially-built-regal-chambers-a-study-suggests-180988899/</guid></item><item><title>巴哈马附近发现的沉船令研究人员着迷，因为它们可能与真正的加勒比海盗有关</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/shipwrecks-discovered-near-the-bahamas-tantalize-researchers-with-possible-ties-to-the-real-pirates-of-the-caribbean-180988901/</link><description>由考古学家和电影制片人组成的团队获准在拿骚港的禁区潜水，发现了六艘沉船，其中三艘疑似与海盗时代有关</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 13:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/shipwrecks-discovered-near-the-bahamas-tantalize-researchers-with-possible-ties-to-the-real-pirates-of-the-caribbean-180988901/</guid></item><item><title>参观纽约一家医院为病童绘制的获救和修复的《爱丽丝梦游仙境》壁画</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-rescued-and-restored-alice-in-wonderland-mural-painted-for-sick-children-at-a-new-york-hospital-180988898/</link><description>艾布拉姆·尚帕尼尔 (Abram Champanier) 的《爱丽丝梦游仙境》是受联邦艺术项目委托创作的，该项目是一项在公共场所倡导美国艺术的新政计划</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 20:24:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-rescued-and-restored-alice-in-wonderland-mural-painted-for-sick-children-at-a-new-york-hospital-180988898/</guid></item><item><title>科学家用冰人奥茨木乃伊尸体上发现的酵母制作酸面包</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-made-sourdough-bread-with-yeast-found-on-otzi-the-icemans-mummified-body-180988894/</link><description>199